net.krglok.realms

  • Packages that use net.krglok.realms 
    Package Description
    net.krglok.realms
    incorporate the plugin definition and the layer of direct access from and to the server also hold the commands for the plugin , separated as clss for each command and subcommand define the task of the plugin
    net.krglok.realms.data  
  • Classes in net.krglok.realms used by net.krglok.realms 
    Class and Description
    CommandRealms
    Command handling for the command registered to the plugin every subCommand is a separate instance of abstract class RealmsCommand allactive commands must be in the cmdList Basic help for no SubCommand are handled in the parser.
    iRealmsCommand
    Interface for the internal commands the command are hanled by the command interpreter - getRequiredArgs , give the number of necessary parameters to the interpreter - setPara(X), for each used datatype is methode installed - getParaTypes , give the datatype info of the parameter by position to the interpreter - canExecute , give true or or false and can individually setup - execute , realize the command individually
    Realms
    Container for the plugin.
    RealmsCommand
    base class for idividual command executed in the plugin.
    RealmsCommandType
    Enum for the reistered commands this are keywords for the command interpreter
    RealmsPermission 
    RealmsSubCommandType
    Enum for the possible subCommands of the plugin this are keywords for the command interpreter
    TaxTask
    realize a day based task (realDay)
    TickTask
    realize the livecycle of the RealmModel normally the tick is 1 second
